name: 10 Inch Dough Bowl Candle
description:
This is a 10-12 oz candle. The entire candle is handmade, down to the bowl which is hand carved by artists.
Hansel & Gretel - A sweet base of vanilla frosting and Tonka Bean supports mid notes of cinnamon sticks, nutmeg, and graham crackers, with top notes of bergamot and cherry.
Pumpkin Souffle - This fragrance is so good the description just doesn't do it justice! A rich pumpkin flavor blended with a fruity bouquet of cherry and mimosa as well as fresh nutmeg, clove, and cinnamon finished off with nuances of caramel, sweet brown sugar, and vanilla.
Creme Brule - This one smells like a rich, creamy French coffee blend
Mahogany Teakwood - Green, citrus, and fruity top notes with floral noes of jasmine, rose, and lily enhanced by sweet woody and musky base notes.
Creamy Vanilla - A rich and creamy blend of coconut and berries with mid notes of soft butter and mimosa all on a bed of sweet vanilla and warm Tonka Bean.

name: 20oz Tall Mug with Flip Lid
description:
The double-wall vacuum-insulated walls give you a worry-free mind knowing your beverages are kept icy cold or piping hot for hours.  Made of lightweight 18/8 food-grade stainless steel that is non-leaching and will not retain taste or odor. The double-wall technology prevents condensation on the outside for those hot sunny days while keeping the heat within the inner wall so you don’t have to worry about burning your hand while holding your mug.

The 20oz tall mug is perfect to use as your everyday coffee cup and is designed to fit in most car cup holders. The easy-grip handle makes it convenient for you to hold while on the go and the double-wall vacuum-insulated technology ensures your hot beverage will stay piping hot and your cold beverages will stay icy cold until the next refill.

The 20oz tall mug includes a screw-on flip lid with a flipping mechanism that clicks in place to keep it splashproof. It has a silicone ring that ensures a snug fit retaining the beverages’ ideal tempe

description: Crunchy, salty pretzels are smothered in a sweet vanilla yogurt coating creating a perfectly indulgent snack. Reach for these when you're craving a salty-sweet option any time of the day. Add to your favorite trail mix, mix them with some nuts, or enjoy on their own!

name: 750ml Double-Wall Vacuum-Insulated Wine Growlers w/Flat Top
description:
The double-wall vacuum-insulated walls give you a worry-free mind knowing your favorite wines are kept at their optimal temperature. Made of lightweight 18/8 food-grade stainless steel that is non-leaching and will not retain taste or odor. The double-wall technology prevents condensation on the outside of the growler so you don’t have to worry about ruining your attire while carrying it by your side.

The wine growler is the ideal traveling companion for transporting your favorite wine or spritzer. With its sleek and narrow design, you can enjoy your elegant social event knowing your growler won't be an eyesore on the beverage table. Holding a full bottle of wine it is ideal to use for sharing with the bridal party or hosting a springtime brunch. The vacuum-insulated walls ensure your wine is kept at its optimal temperature amid each pour. The double-wall technology prevents sweating on the outside of the bottle, so you don't have to worry about it leaving a water ring on your table.

name: Frother for Perfect Latte Prep
description:
This nifty re-chargable milk frother is hands down our favorite way to prep Clevr! Why? Let us count the ways:


* No clean up—just rinse under running water after use.
* Amazing texture—makes a smooth, creamy latte + perfect microfoam, every time.
* Mixes fast—zero to latte in 10 seconds.
* Adventure ready—the perfect cup, wherever you are! Camping, road-trips, travel, or at your desk.
* No batteries needed—USB re-chargable for the win!
To prepare: add your Clevr latte blend and hot water to a mug. Froth for 10 seconds, or until latte is smooth. Sip and smile!

Prep Tips:

* Make sure your cup is big enough so the latte has room to froth without spilling over! Around 1/2 full should be perfect.
* If using a smaller cup, just froth with half your water, then add the remaining water.
* For extra fancy prep: we sometimes like to froth our lattes in a barista jug, then pour into a mug. Totally unnecessary, but makes you feel posh.

name: Two Pack | Coco Coir Pole for Plant Support (Large)
description:
Ideal plant support for indoor climbing plants and vines while maintaining moisture for aerial roots absorption. Made from natural and biodegradable coconut husk, the pole is safe and sturdy for training climbing plants Monsteras to grow upright. As your plant grow bigger, new poles are easily stacked on top of each other to accommodate the new height.
What is coco coir?
Coco coir is a byproduct of coconut processing leaving behind fibrous coconut husk.  Although the properties are similar to peat moss in terms of weight and texture, however, coco coir is much more environmentally friendly than peat moss with less impact on the ecosystem.
Large Coco Coir Pole:
Measurements: 2in Diameter x 11in height (5in wooden stake height)
